sequenceDiagram
    participant ESP as ESP32 (IoT)
    participant MQTT as Mosquitto
    participant BR as mqtt-bridge
    participant API as API + game-logic
    participant FS as front_screen (R3F + Rapier)
    participant BS as back_screen
    participant DMD as dmd_screen

    Note over ESP,DMD: Sélection & démarrage (mode boss / solo PvE)
    BS->>API: ScreenEnvelope start_game {mode, players[]}
    API->>API: GameEvent::StartGame → GameState (lives, PveState boss 0)
    API->>BR: WsMessage Outbound GameState {state:"start"}
    BR->>MQTT: pub pinball/<id>/game/state (retain)
    MQTT->>ESP: sub game/state

    Note over ESP,DMD: Lancement de la bille (plunger)
    ESP->>MQTT: pub input/plunger {position, released:true}
    MQTT->>BR: sub input/plunger
    BR->>API: WsMessage Inbound Plunger
    API-->>FS: routage → spawn + impulsion bille (force = position)

    Note over ESP,DMD: Flipper hardware
    ESP->>MQTT: pub input/button {id:"flipper_left", state:1}
    MQTT->>BR: sub input/button
    BR->>API: WsMessage Inbound Button
    API-->>FS: GameEvent::ButtonPressed → active flipper
    FS->>FS: Rapier applique l'impulsion

    Note over FS,DMD: Collision détectée côté physique (front)
    FS->>API: ScreenEnvelope ball_hit {hits:[{id,type,force}]}
    API->>API: scoring + combo.detector → ComboEffect, BossDefeated?
    API->>BR: WsMessage Outbound BallHit {hits[]}
    BR->>MQTT: pub ball/hit
    MQTT->>ESP: sub ball/hit → profil vibration (bumper/rail/slingshot...)
    API-->>DMD: broadcast ScoreUpdate {score, multiplier}
    API-->>BS: broadcast ScoreDelta + ComboActivated

    Note over ESP,DMD: Boss touché (mode PvE)
    API->>API: Boss.take_hit(dmg) → HealthComponent
    alt boss vaincu
        API->>API: PvePhase Transition → boss suivant / Victory
        API-->>DMD: broadcast LifeUpdate + nouveau boss
    end

    Note over ESP,DMD: Gyroscope / Tilt
    ESP->>MQTT: pub input/gyro {ax,ay,az, tilt:true}
    MQTT->>BR: sub input/gyro
    BR->>API: WsMessage Inbound Gyro
    API->>API: TiltState.on_tilt → Penalty puis cheating_detected

    Note over ESP,DMD: Bille perdue
    FS->>API: ScreenEnvelope ball_lost {ball, player}
    API->>API: GameEvent::BallLost → lives--
    alt vies restantes
        API->>BR: Outbound GameState {state:"ball_lost"}
        BR->>MQTT: pub game/state
        FS->>FS: BallSaver / replace bille
    else dernière vie (NoLivesLeft)
        API->>API: GameEvent::GameOverTriggered
        API->>BR: Outbound GameState {state:"game_over"}
        BR->>MQTT: pub game/state (retain)
        MQTT->>ESP: sub game/state
        API-->>BS: broadcast EndGame
        API-->>DMD: broadcast EndGame + high_score
    end

